#: ../../B/Befunge.rst:5
msgid "Befunge"
msgstr "Befunge"

#: ../../B/Befunge.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../B/Befunge.rst:9
msgid ""
"A worthy companion to :ref:`INTERCAL`\\; a computer language family which "
"escapes the quotidian limitation of linear control flow and embraces program"
" counters flying through multiple dimensions with exotic topologies. The "
"Befunge home page is at `http://www.catseye.mb.ca/esoteric/befunge/ "
"<http://www.catseye.mb.ca/esoteric/befunge/>`_."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`INTERCAL`\\ "
"にふさわしい仲間。線形の制御フローという日常的な制約から逃れ、風変わりな位相幾何学のもと複数の次元を飛び回るプログラムカウンターを擁するコンピューター言語ファミリー。Befungeのホームページは"
" `http://www.catseye.mb.ca/esoteric/befunge/ "
"<http://www.catseye.mb.ca/esoteric/befunge/>`_ にある。"
